{"tid":538798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去年29名警員被捕　盧偉聰強調只佔整體不足0.1%","createTime":"2018-01-24T03:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T05:46:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84f680c906bd8ebc21ca369b3ca5e2c9a0acf5eb","tid":538798,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"【去年29名警員被捕　盧偉聰強調只佔整體不足0.1%】<br />\n<br />\n警方今日（1月23日）公佈去年的罪案數字，本港去年整體罪案有56017宗，較前年下跌7.6%，是自1975年以來新低，總破案率為48.2%，上升0.9%<br />\n<br />\n至於最受關注的警員犯案數字，警務處處長盧偉聰表示，去年共有29名警員涉及不同罪案，較前年43人少。當中15人涉及刑事案，3人涉及非刑事案件，其餘11人則被其他部門拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰重申，警隊重視警務人員操守，會透過誠信管理委員會處理，他又強調，被捕人數佔整體警員不足0.1%，絕大部分警員每日都盡忠職守。"},{"pid":"27e2e519e83ca9a72ca217abe7975fe39f4131d5","tid":538798,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"有一個已經唔應該"},{"pid":"25a683c7f317421f42a4721e9cf1b34430bada77","tid":538798,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"用職業犯罪率去計係唔係排第一？"},{"pid":"57f0d8df5a776eb637cfd1f2e42d3d4f950bf41e","tid":538798,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67acd6059987318218a6f22cca9ace625c5b5788","tid":538798,"uid":53118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/113059_f35a8d7adb66ec7554d5f21f3a92b124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F113059_f35a8d7adb66ec7554d5f21f3a92b124.jpg&h=f7184637&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cffcb392bab3b7a9825b155a2863393cd007d26","tid":538798,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"繼續請幾千人刷低個%<br />\n點可以扼殺前線警員既努力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地為市民入冊嫁<br />\n支持警超聯繼續入球<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" cla